title: Bread Machine Rye Bread
ingredients: ['200ml water', '3/4 teaspoon cider vinegar', '200g strong bread flour', '50g rye flour', '25g oat bran', '15g butter', '1 1/2 tablespoons caster sugar', '1 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon caraway seeds', '1 teaspoon dried minced onion', '2 tablespoons unsweetened cocoa powder', '1 teaspoon dried active baking yeast']
